<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 20:08:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拉比德尔芬·霍维耶尔 (Delphine Horveilleur)：“犹太复国主义关乎力量。 10 月 7 日之后，以色列人理解了破碎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-28/ty-article-podcast/zionisms-narrative-is-about-strength-after-oct-7-israelis-understand-brokenness/0000018f-c01b-d053-a1bf-ec1f063f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-28/ty-article-podcast/zionisms-narrative-is-about-strength-after-oct-7-israelis-understand-brokenness/0000018f-c01b-d053-a1bf-ec1f063f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生官员：拉法帐篷营地的新袭击造成 21 人死亡；以色列国防军否认打击区域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-officials-21-dead-in-new-israeli-attack-on-tent-camp-in-west-rafah/0000018f-bfc0-dfeb-a58f-bffa1c4f0000</link><description>据卫生部称，共有64人受伤，其中10人伤势严重。市政府官员表示，袭击发生在以色列国防军指定为安全区的地区</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:22:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-officials-21-dead-in-new-israeli-attack-on-tent-camp-in-west-rafah/0000018f-bfc0-dfeb-a58f-bffa1c4f0000</guid></item><item><title>《卫报》：以色列多年来一直在监视国际刑事法院首席检察官，包括最近几个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-guardian-israel-spied-for-years-on-icc-chief-prosecutor-including-in-recent-months/0000018f-bfe0-dfeb-a58f-bffa942f0000</link><description>《卫报》、Local Call 和 +972 的调查揭露了以色列涉嫌针对国际刑事法院及其官员的秘密行动。内塔尼亚胡被描述为“痴迷于”针对他的案件，而据报道，前摩萨德主席约西·科恩在秘密会议上威胁前首席检察官</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-guardian-israel-spied-for-years-on-icc-chief-prosecutor-including-in-recent-months/0000018f-bfe0-dfeb-a58f-bffa942f0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军将军亚伊尔·戈兰横扫工党选举，誓言团结以色列分裂的左翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-general-yair-golan-clinches-labor-party-election-vows-to-rally-israels-fractured-left/0000018f-c047-dade-adef-ecefdf300000</link><description>戈兰以 95% 的选票获胜，工党议员支持他的竞选，旨在团结以色列犹太复国主义左翼。他在胜选演说中表示，我们将全力以赴推翻政府并推进选举</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-general-yair-golan-clinches-labor-party-election-vows-to-rally-israels-fractured-left/0000018f-c047-dade-adef-ecefdf300000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯兰圣战组织播放加沙被囚禁人质的视频；以色列官员：人质谈判没有取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/islamic-jihad-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-c030-dade-adef-ecbb7ce30000</link><description>25 岁的萨沙·特鲁帕诺夫 (Sasha Trupanov) 与他的祖母、母亲和伴侣一起从他位于尼尔奥兹基布兹的家中被带走。目前尚不清楚该视频何时拍摄。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 17:20:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/islamic-jihad-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-c030-dade-adef-ecbb7ce30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 235 天：伊斯兰圣战组织播放以色列人质萨沙·特鲁帕诺夫的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-235-islamic-jihad-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-sasha-trupanov/0000018f-bff3-d475-a5cf-ffffbb490001</link><description>以色列国防军表示，现在确定拉法帐篷营地致命火灾的原因“还为时过早” ■ 爱尔兰、西班牙和挪威正式承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织发布以色列人质萨沙·特鲁帕诺夫的视频 ■ 前摩萨德负责人约西·科恩威胁前国际刑事法院检察官辞职《卫报》报道，针对以色列的战争罪调查 ■ 战争进入 235 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-235-islamic-jihad-airs-video-of-israeli-hostage-sasha-trupanov/0000018f-bff3-d475-a5cf-ffffbb490001</guid></item><item><title>唯一仍在购买以色列军队版本的拉法罢工的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-only-ones-who-still-believe-israeli-armys-latest-reports-on-rafah/0000018f-bfa5-df6b-a3ff-ffaf75350000</link><description>以色列媒体一直在隐瞒加沙战争中令人难以忍受的数字和图片。军队关于拉法罢工的最新公告也应该持怀疑态度。除非你是以色列媒体的忠实消费者</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-only-ones-who-still-believe-israeli-armys-latest-reports-on-rafah/0000018f-bfa5-df6b-a3ff-ffaf75350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队正在调查空袭后武器爆炸是否在拉法帐篷营地引发致命火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/idf-probes-if-weapons-explosion-ignited-rafah-camp-fire-after-attack-on-hamas-officials/0000018f-bff7-df6b-a3ff-ffffc2580000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人表示，两名哈马斯官员在没有平民的院落中遭到袭击后，拉法发生致命火灾，原因仍不清楚。加沙卫生官员报告称，事件中有 45 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 16:28:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/idf-probes-if-weapons-explosion-ignited-rafah-camp-fire-after-attack-on-hamas-officials/0000018f-bff7-df6b-a3ff-ffffc2580000</guid></item><item><title>“他们放弃了我们”：以色列北部边境城镇负责人要求以色列国防军和政府脱离接触</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/head-of-north-israel-border-town-demands-disengagement-from-idf-government/0000018f-bf72-dfeb-a58f-bffacbd00000</link><description>在真主党再次发动猛烈导弹袭击后，莫沙夫·马加利奥特主席埃坦·戴维迪表示，他希望立即撤走士兵和以色列国防军指挥中心。他宣布：“我们将自己处理事情”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/head-of-north-israel-border-town-demands-disengagement-from-idf-government/0000018f-bf72-dfeb-a58f-bffacbd00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长指责西班牙总理在西班牙承认巴勒斯坦国之日“煽动对犹太人的种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-fm-spanish-pm-guilty-of-incitement-to-genocide-of-jews-for-recognizing-palestine/0000018f-bf59-dfeb-a58f-bffbf8920000</link><description>西班牙首相在宣布承认这一决定时表示，“我们不会针对任何人做出这一决定，尤其是针对以色列，我们希望与以色列建立尽可能最好的关系。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-fm-spanish-pm-guilty-of-incitement-to-genocide-of-jews-for-recognizing-palestine/0000018f-bf59-dfeb-a58f-bffbf8920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方因涉嫌贿赂和欺诈而拘留并调查前法院院长、高级律师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigate-ex-court-president-top-attorney-for-suspected-bribery-fraud/0000018f-bf37-d19e-a19f-fff788910000</link><description>调查人员从前特拉维夫地区法院院长和前以色列律师协会主席的家中没收了文件，然后将他们带到国家欺诈调查组。两个月前，《国土报》披露了两人进行交换的录音。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:14:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigate-ex-court-president-top-attorney-for-suspected-bribery-fraud/0000018f-bf37-d19e-a19f-fff788910000</guid></item><item><title>犹太机构拒绝在耶路撒冷骄傲游行期间悬挂 LGBTQ 旗帜的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/jewish-agency-rejects-plea-to-fly-lgbtq-flag-during-jerusalems-pride-parade/0000018f-bf03-dfeb-a58f-bffb61590000</link><description>这一请求的灵感来自于犹太复国主义大会通过的“历史性决议”，该决议“支持全世界 LGBTQ 群体与以色列之间的联系”。在拒绝后，犹太机构重申，它“每天都尊重并包容[其]社区的所有成员”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/jewish-agency-rejects-plea-to-fly-lgbtq-flag-during-jerusalems-pride-parade/0000018f-bf03-dfeb-a58f-bffb61590000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是否会在梅洛尼领导的意大利失去一个重要的右翼盟友？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-losing-a-key-right-wing-ally-in-melonis-italy/0000018f-bece-d5c5-a3ff-ffeff8270000</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼是 10 月 7 日之后首批公开支持以色列的世界领导人之一。现在，就连她也与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡保持距离，并公开谈论巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:26:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-losing-a-key-right-wing-ally-in-melonis-italy/0000018f-bece-d5c5-a3ff-ffeff8270000</guid></item><item><title>礼貌的以色列定居者礼貌地剥夺巴勒斯坦人的财产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-polite-israeli-settlers-who-courteously-dispossess-palestinians/0000018f-ba79-d19e-a19f-fefb8c710000</link><description>在西岸的一些地区，穿着军装的定居者在驱逐农地所有者的同时避免暴力</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/the-polite-israeli-settlers-who-courteously-dispossess-palestinians/0000018f-ba79-d19e-a19f-fefb8c710000</guid></item><item><title>“我会把他们赶出去”：特朗普告诉犹太捐助者他将驱逐亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/i-will-throw-them-out-trump-tells-jewish-donors-hell-deport-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-bebb-d19e-a19f-fefb8d910000</link><description>在与捐助者的闭门会议上，特朗普承诺如果当选，将迅速对学生抗议者采取行动，同时确认以色列有权进行“反恐战争”，这与之前呼吁结束战争的声明相矛盾</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/i-will-throw-them-out-trump-tells-jewish-donors-hell-deport-pro-palestinian-protesters/0000018f-bebb-d19e-a19f-fefb8d910000</guid></item><item><title>德国裔以色列人入籍申请激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/naturalization-applications-surge-from-israelis-with-german-roots/0000018f-be7f-d19e-a19f-feff477d0000</link><description>报告显示，今年1月至4月共收到6,869份申请，而2023年全年收到9,129份申请，2022年收到5,670份申请</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/naturalization-applications-surge-from-israelis-with-german-roots/0000018f-be7f-d19e-a19f-feff477d0000</guid></item><item><title>总检察长称，本-格维尔传唤谴责以色列警察局长是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/hearing-ben-gvir-is-set-to-hold-for-israels-police-chief-is-illegal-ag-says/0000018f-be36-df6b-a3ff-fe3eaecd0000</link><description>总检察长表示，传唤警察局长引发了人们的担忧，因为本-格维尔试图惩罚他，因为他阻止他干预警察工作，这与高等法院的裁决相矛盾。她写道：“有人担心你想以他为榜样来威慑整个警察指挥链。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:53:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/hearing-ben-gvir-is-set-to-hold-for-israels-police-chief-is-illegal-ag-says/0000018f-be36-df6b-a3ff-fe3eaecd0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么加沙的死亡人数可能比报道的要高</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/rising-fatality-numbers-in-gaza-are-in-all-probability-higher-than-reported/0000018f-bab5-de04-a58f-bab5ea1d0000</link><description>杀戮的范围以及由于缺乏基本卫生条件、食品和医疗服务而导致的疾病和死亡发生率，需要在以色列进行紧急公开辩论</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/rising-fatality-numbers-in-gaza-are-in-all-probability-higher-than-reported/0000018f-bab5-de04-a58f-bab5ea1d0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯国家恳求欧盟高级官员承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-implore-senior-eu-officials-to-recognize-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-be1b-df6b-a3ff-fe3b5e0a0000</link><description>多个阿拉伯国家的高级官员在布鲁塞尔举行会谈，呼吁欧盟国家加入爱尔兰、挪威和西班牙的声明，并对以色列对美国与沙特阿拉伯的正常化协议大纲的反应表示失望</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 08:27:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-implore-senior-eu-officials-to-recognize-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-be1b-df6b-a3ff-fe3b5e0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击拉法后，致命大火在加沙人中蔓延绝望和悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</link><description>加沙卫生当局称，有 45 人死亡，其中大部分是妇女、儿童和老人。一名难民营居民说：“在巴勒斯坦，我们的孩子、长辈、妇女和家园每天都在燃烧”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 07:37:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-28/ty-article/deadly-fire-spreads-despair-grief-among-gazans-after-israeli-strike/0000018f-be05-d475-a5cf-feffa1ee0000</guid></item></channel></rss>